<plot>Ernst Held is managing a hotel together with his posh, suppressive wife, but is more interested in writing poetry. When Ernst is apparently "caught in the act" with a woman who he was just reading his poems to, he flees to Munich, trying to find a new job - as a waiter and as a poet.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?237335</url></doc>
